* Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ʌɡ|-ʌɡ]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# a large [[cup]], usually having a [[handle]] and used without a [[saucer]]
# (''slang'') the [[face]], often used deprecatingly
#: ''What an ugly '''mug'''.''
# (''colloquial'') A person who is easily [[fool]]ed.
#: ''Do you take me for a '''mug'''?''

